<div class="col-xl-8 col-lg-8 col-md-12 col-12 content-section" id="content_section_1">
    <div class="service__details__wraper">
        <div class="service__details__heading text__gradient" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-duration="1500">
            <h4>The Development of Businesses</h4>
        </div>
        <div class="service__details__planning__inner service__details__text" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-duration="1500">
            <p>The Business Development group is largely responsible for maintaining current client relationships, identifying and recruiting new investors to TD-ICAV, and maintaining established ties with those investors. People from a wide variety of fields, including academic finance, investment consultancy, and institutional money management, comprise the group. In addition to providing prospects and customers with information about NEW-VC-NAME as a business, the members of the group are able to provide specific insights into the investment process and execution, current portfolio positioning, and research developments. Their collective vast variety of abilities makes this possible.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<div class="col-xl-8 col-lg-8 col-md-12 col-12 content-section" id="content_section_2" >
    <div class="service__details__wraper">
        <div class="service__details__heading text__gradient" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-duration="1500">
            <h4>Engineering and Technology</h4>
        </div>
        <div class="service__details__planning__inner service__details__text" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-duration="1500">
            <p>At TD-ICAV, the engineering team, which accounts for 26% of the company's workforce, is actively involved in all parts of our business operations. Our order to design solutions that will not only help the business in the present but will also serve to expand and flourish in the future, our engineers work in collaboration with portfolio managers at every level, beginning with the conception of signals and ending with the execution of transactions. Our engineers help us successfully communicate performance by facilitating data visualization and reporting of world-class quality. They also help us effectively convey performance. Moreover, they are in charge of developing the systems and procedures that support risk management, reporting, and overall company operations. The team also ensured the smooth operation of the entire organization by managing the complex data lifecycle and supplying the daily productivity tools. </p>
            <p>We host these tools, which include operating systems and communications, either on the premises or in the cloud. Our security engineers are responsible for safeguarding each and every one of these products from harm. Engineers at NEW-VC-NAME experience the entire lifecycle of their products, starting from their conception and concluding with their disposal.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<div class="col-xl-8 col-lg-8 col-md-12 col-12 content-section" id="content_section_3">
