            <p>The Facilities team is in charge of a wide range of essential services that are critical to the business's performance. This category of services includes the management of buildings and vendors, the provision of security and contingency plans, the coordination of space and construction, the supply of facilities and amenities, and the provision of reception and administrative assistance are all items that fall under this category of services.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<div class="col-xl-8 col-lg-8 col-md-12 col-12 content-section" id="content_section_4">
