            <h4> Finance Team</h4>
        </div>
        <div class="service__details__planning__inner service__details__text" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-duration="1500">
            <p>TD-ICAV's finance team is responsible for maintaining the necessary financial paperwork for the corporate entities it owns. Payroll, accounts payable, treasury, accounts receivable, internal and external financial and regulatory reporting, procurement, and tax are all areas covered by their jurisdiction. Furthermore, this team is responsible for managing relationships with TD-ICAV's customers, third-party providers, financial institutions, and other counterparties.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<div class="col-xl-8 col-lg-8 col-md-12 col-12 content-section" id="content_section_5">
    <div class="service__details__wraper">
        <div class="service__details__heading text__gradient" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-duration="1500">
            <h4>Human Resources</h4>
        </div>
        <div class="service__details__planning__inner service__details__text" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-duration="1500">
            <p>The Human Resources department is in charge of the company's efforts to recruit, retain, and reward outstanding talent, as well as cultivate it. In order to provide a full suite of services, the team works together with each of the company's businesses to provide services such as workforce planning and recruiting, best practices for engaging and rewarding workers, the creation of competitive compensation and benefit programs, and employee advancement and development. Furthermore, human resources is responsible for providing management with counsel, developing initiatives to improve employee engagement and organizational culture, and supervising TD-ICAV, which is the organization's own learning and development program for workers.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<div class="col-xl-8 col-lg-8 col-md-12 col-12 content-section" id="content_section_6">
    <div class="service__details__wraper">
        <div class="service__details__heading text__gradient" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-duration="1500">
