        </div>
        <div class="service__details__planning__inner service__details__text" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-duration="1500">
            <h5>Legal Team</h5>
            <p>The legal team plays the role of an internal adviser, providing direction and oversight to all divisions within the corporation. The group assumes the responsibility of supervising both newly enacted and altered laws, while also offering guidance and assistance on a wide range of business-related matters. In addition to this, the team is now involved in the process of negotiating contracts and developing the structural framework for new goods that are linked with new business divisions.</p>
            <h5>Compliance Team</h5>
            <p>The compliance team at TD-ICAV not only fulfills legal, regulatory, and fiduciary requirements, but also upholds the high ethical standards expected of all its workers. In addition to training and ongoing compliance education, the team is responsible for developing policies and procedures, identifying and guiding risks for business and operational entities, and providing regulatory compliance education. The compliance team at TD-ICAV draws additional attention to the fact that the company is committed to maintaining a culture of compliance in the face of a constantly shifting legal and regulatory environment.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<div class="col-xl-8 col-lg-8 col-md-12 col-12 content-section" id="content_section_7">
    <div class="service__details__wraper">
