        <div class="service__details__planning__inner service__details__text" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-duration="1500">
            <p>The marketing team is in charge of the company's brand management, corporate communications, digital strategy, design, and signature events as a part of business development. Additionally, they are responsible for the company's hallmark events. Utilizing a global communications platform to target all investment plans, locations, and client channels is the means by which it intends to accomplish its goal of increasing the company's visibility as well as acquiring and retaining clients. The marketing team is committed to offering the most innovative, scalable, and successful means of presenting the distinctive qualities of NEW-VC-NAME. These qualities include the company's competence in the business, its investment skills, the client solutions it offers, and its strong partnerships with the most prestigious academic institutions.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<div class="col-xl-8 col-lg-8 col-md-12 col-12 content-section" id="content_section_8">
    <div class="service__details__wraper">
        <div class="service__details__heading text__gradient" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-duration="1500">
            <h4>Operations Team</h4>
        </div>
        <div class="service__details__planning__inner service__details__text" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-duration="1500">
            <p>Operations is responsible for providing support for the company's trading, investing, and reporting operations. The operations team primarily aims to maintain a regulated operating environment, develop scalable investment procedures, and provide excellent support to both internal and external customers. In addition, the team offers assistance in the planning and implementation of firm-wide projects, as well as undertaking operational due diligence, managing counterparties, and engaging in activities connected to clients.</p>
